body:
This Resource Pack changes crops & farm-related plants of the game to be more good looking.

----

This pack changes:
- The hoes;
- The seeds;
- The crops;
- The bone meal;
- The honey related items and blocks;

----

{**This is a part of a major minecraft Resource Pack who I am making who will be called "Minecraft Reforged".**}

